OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly dry
OL,6,Fstart to the evening in east
OL,7,FAberdeenshire and Aberdeen city.
OL,8,FOtherwise, cloudy with outbreaks of
OL,9,Frain spreading east, these heavy and
OL,10,Fthundery at times and continuing
OL,11,Fovernight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FAny overnight heavy rain
OL,14,Fsoon clearing east in the morning.
OL,15,FOtherwise cool, dull and cloudy with
OL,16,Fsome patchy light drizzle possible.
